{"tid":1435194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[旅行準備] 記得帶多件藍衫呀","createTime":"2019-08-09T03:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T03:57:25.000Z","uid":283166,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a4fbcd2e9e6658540cc3a7127eeeebb4b9067b09","tid":1435194,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:36:31.000Z","msg":"聽日入大埔的，記得帶多件藍衫呀，<br />\n黑衫太吸熱，要有替換衣物。<br />\n萬一遇到犬類，就記得換衫啦，<br />\n唔擔保唔咬，<br />\n但萬一被追或咬，記得影低上傳呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZPQP65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZPQP65.jpg&h=e8b9af07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a64c892ecac091c83e3917a4089b3d5cff2ede7","tid":1435194,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:37:19.000Z","msg":"去旅行做足準備"},{"pid":"209e366728173fe221e57e102b334fa2db968dfb","tid":1435194,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:37:21.000Z","msg":"8.9 機場萬人接機<br />\n開始時間： 2019年8月9日下午1 點起<br />\n地點 ： 一號客運大樓機場接機大堂<br />\n1. 不申請不反對通知書<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 和平靜坐，不衝擊不破壞不入禁區</span><br />\n3. Be water<br />\n4. 促政府答應五大訴求<br />\n5. 停止暴力打壓示威遊行<br />\n少你一個真係少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日1:00 機場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06Qc3tF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06Qc3tF.png&h=8bf84c52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fecca4cf79d3e0da930e7d18e7bd2eaa417e9fae","tid":1435194,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"阿婆豆腐花"},{"pid":"464b1224fc5d3438d9094158d0bf0779e8fdd492","tid":1435194,"uid":34020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:39:35.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位做文宣，好人一生平安<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEvo5Ws.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEvo5Ws.